'''Ayt Sɣruccn''' tga yat taqbilt tamaziɣt [[wp/zgh/taznatit|taznatit]] izdɣn ɣ idurar n [[Aṭlas anammas|waṭlas anammas]] (fazaz) ɣ [[Lmɣrib|umrruk]]. Ils nna s sawaln ar as ttinin "tasɣruccnit", awal ad ikcm ɣ tantliwin n tutlayt [[Tamaziɣt n Waṭlas anammas|tamaziɣt waṭlas anammas]] ɣ [[Lmɣrib|umrruk]]. 

== Amzruy ==
Traran Ayt Sɣruccn aẓur nnsn s umzwaru nnsn [[Wp/zgh/mulay ɛli bnɛmr|Mulay ɛli bnɛmr]], zzigs ay d ikka yism n tqbilt ad, ar ttinin ɣ "lusṭura" mas is ikka t inn umzwaru nnsn ig agrram yan wass ttuɣ t iksa, lliɣ iqqim ar ittẓalla yudf as d wuccn ulli nns, yasi afus issɣar t. Aylliɣ as gan Sɣruccn zɛma "sɣr + uccn = sɣruccn"

== Iɣsan d udɣar n uzdduɣ ==
[[Afaylu:عين الحجر تازوطة آيت جراد - panoramio.jpg |thumb|300px|ɛin lḥjr ayt sɣruccn, bulman]]
Tbḍa tqbilt n ayt sɣruccn f amẓn yan n udɣar imɣarn zɣ [[Fas]] ar [[Mlwyt tamatuyt]].

* '''Ayt sɣruccn ḥarira''', llan ɣ ugmuḍ n tmdint n [[Fas]] ɣ ubrid s [[Fas]], ɣ yiɣrman amm llwata, aɣbalu aqurar...

* '''Ayt sɣruccn n imuzzar''', llan unẓul (iffus) i [[Fas]], iɣrman nnsn imqqurn gant Imuzzar n Knḍr, Ayt Ssbɛ, Sidi Xyyar...

* '''Ayt sɣruccn n ticcukt''', ḍfurn i tsga n Bulman, illa mad ittinin mas d nitni aygan aẓur n Ayt Sɣruccn, acku ar ttinin mas umi d yusa babatsn (mulay ɛli bnɛmr) iga u [[Fas]] issrs ɣ tmazirt ad, zɣ iɣrman nnsn ɣ tsga ad: Skkura mdaz, Bulman, Lmrs, Ayt ɛbdlla...

* '''Ayt sɣruccn n tlssint''': imsasa wattayn n imrza is iga iɣrm n ɣzwan illan idis i tlssint ɣ ugmuḍ n umrruk (tasga n ifyyey (figig)) asnsu amzwaru n imzwura n Ayt Sɣruccn s umata, ar ɣila suln rzzfn dars ayt sɣruccn s akk tisggwin.

